The_Japan_Foundation_Center for Cultural_Exchange in Vietnam proudly presents Japanese_Film_Festival 2015 : Colors of Love from 9 October – 14 November 2015 in Ho_Chi_Minh_City , Danang and Hanoi .
Japanese_Film_Festival is one of the most anticipated annual events of the Japan_Foundation and it is widely known that its free tickets are quickly ran out in few days , thanks to the enthusiastic Japanese film fans in Vietnam .
This year ’ s film festival focuses on the introduction of Japanese films under the theme of “ Shape of Heart ” . We will screen Six_Japanese films , which portray various shapes of hearts , loves among friends , families , lovers . The festival ’ s opener is “ Beyond the Memories ” ( 2013/dir . SHINJO Takehiko ) .
All films will be screened with both English and Vietnamese sub - titles . The admission is free , but audience is advised to obtain free tickets at following venues .
Film_Festival_Information :
